title: Passalo function not working when using through the C# code
body:
I am using SDL Passolo 2016. Using Passolo automation I am not able to import previously exported file using prj.ImportTransBundle(fileToBeImported). The same file if importing manually, is being successfully imported. Using Passolo automation I have used both the flag pslImportMerge and pslImportRelease still am not able to do it.

Not sure here how to proceed here and any help is appreciated. Thanks
